OL,3,CRacist texts about slaves and 'picking
OL,4,Ccotton' sent to black people in the US
OL,6,FUS authorities are investigating
OL,7,Freports of black people receiving
OL,8,Fracist text messages from unrecognised
OL,9,Fphone numbers telling them they have
OL,10,Fbeen "selected to pick cotton at the
OL,11,Fnearest plantation".
OL,13,FThe texts, which also referenced
OL,14,F"slave catchers", appeared automated.
OL,15,FBut some who have responded to the
OL,16,Fsender said they received further
OL,17,Ftexts from them.
