OL,3,CRacist texts about slaves and 'picking
OL,4,Ccotton' sent to black people in the US
OL,6,FState attorneys and police have vowed
OL,7,Fto find those responsible for the
OL,8,Fmessages, which have been received in
OL,9,Fmore than a dozen states by black
OL,10,Fchildren, students and working
OL,11,Fprofessionals.
OL,13,FArleta McCall said her daughter, who
OL,14,Fis in her first year at the University
OL,15,Fof Alabama, was "in tears" after
OL,16,Freceiving one of the texts.
