OL,6,FShe told: "It's eerie that it's the
OL,7,Fday after the election. It's eerie
OL,8,Fthat it came to my daughter's personal
OL,9,Fphone. It's eerie that it's only going
OL,10,Fto Black students."
OL,12,FThe FBI said it was "aware" of "the
OL,13,Foffensive and racist text messages
OL,14,Fsent to individuals around the country
OL,15,Fand is in contact with the Justice
OL,16,FDepartment and other federal
OL,17,Fauthorities on the matter".
