OL,3,CRacist texts about slaves and 'picking
OL,4,Ccotton' sent to black people in the US
OL,6,FSome of the messages appear to have
OL,7,Fbeen sent through phone service app
OL,8,FTextNow, which lets users anonymously
OL,9,Fsend texts to people through phone
OL,10,Fnumbers appearing to be randomly
OL,11,Fgenerated.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for TextNow said it
OL,14,Fbelieves a "widespread, coordinated
OL,15,Fattack" had taken place.
OL,17,F"As soon as we became aware, our Trust
OL,18,F& Safety team acted quickly, rapidly
OL,19,Fdisabling the related accounts in less
OL,20,Fthan an hour," a statement said.
