OL,6,FTalaya Jones, a Black resident of New
OL,7,FJersey who received one of the texts,
OL,8,Fsaid: "My initial reaction was
OL,9,Fprobably like disbelief, like I
OL,10,Fthought it was like a joke.
OL,12,F"It really just shows that we didn't
OL,13,Fcome as far as everybody thought we
OL,14,Fdid as a nation, from back in the day
OL,15,Fwhen slavery was still a thing."
