OL,6,FDonald Trump's presidential campaign
OL,7,Fspokesperson said the president elect
OL,8,Fhas nothing to do with the messages.
OL,10,FNew York's Attorney General Letitia
OL,11,FJames called the messages "disgusting"
OL,12,Fand "unacceptable".
OL,14,F"I unequivocally condemn any attempt
OL,15,Fto intimidate or threaten New Yorkers
OL,16,Fand their families," she said.
